machine till this morning.

1839
01:28:38,313 --> 01:28:39,488
Oh, well, wait a minute.

1840
01:28:39,531 --> 01:28:40,489
I thought
that you had the gift.

1841
01:28:40,532 --> 01:28:43,143
Yes, but only a teeny piece.

1842
01:28:43,187 --> 01:28:47,104
[ Sighs ] I missed you.

1843
